WEBVTT

00:00:00.954 --> 00:00:08.319
It is very fashionable and proper 
to speak about food


00:00:08.319 --> 00:00:15.529
in all its forms, all its colors, 
aromas and tastes.

00:00:15.529 --> 00:00:21.183
But after the food goes through 
the digestive system,

00:00:21.183 --> 00:00:24.429
when it is thrown out as crap,

00:00:24.429 --> 00:00:28.026
it is no longer fashionable
to speak about it.

00:00:28.026 --> 00:00:32.685
It is rather revolting.